<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bulk Product Upload</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Bulk Product Upload</h1>
    <p>An admin user can select a file with bulk product data in JSON format (or more such as CSV or text) and upload it into the database.</p>
    
    <form action="/upload" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">
        <h2>Upload Product Data</h2>
        <p>Please select a file to upload:</p>
        <input type="file" name="productData" accept=".json, .csv, .txt">
        <p>Accepted file formats: JSON, CSV, TXT</p>
        <p>Example JSON file format:</p>
        <pre>
[
  {
    "name": "Product 1",
    "description": "Description of Product 1",
    "price": 19.99,
    "category": "Category 1"
  },
  {
    "name": "Product 2",
    "description": "Description of Product 2",
    "price": 29.99,
    "category": "Category 2"
  }
]
        </pre>
        <button type="submit">Upload File</button>
    </form>
</body>
</html>